'''馬克斯·凯斯·布朗利'''（{{lang-en|Marques Keith Brownlee}}；{{bd|1993年|12月3日}}），藝名「'''MKBHD'''」，是一名[[YouTuber|YouTuber]]、[[科技|科技]]評論員、[[網紅|網紅]]及專業[[終極飛盤|終極飛盤]]運動員，以他的科技[[YouTube|YouTube]]頻道MKBHD知名<ref name=autogenerated2>{{cite web|url=https://plus.google.com/+VicGundotra/posts/LMY858eYL7y|title=New MKBHD Video is live! I spend a lot of time in thought for this one - I…|work=google.com|access-date=2016-01-18|archive-date=2016-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161109200138/https://plus.google.com/+VicGundotra/posts/LMY858eYL7y|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="autogenerated1">{{cite web|url=http://pocketnow.com/2013/10/25/pocketnow-vip-episode-3-mkbhd|title=Pocketnow VIP, episode 3: meet Marques Brownlee from MKBHD! - Pocketnow|author=Michael Fisher|date=October 25, 2013|work=Pocketnow|access-date=2016-01-18|archive-date=2018-07-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180715094048/http://pocketnow.com/2013/10/25/pocketnow-vip-episode-3-mkbhd|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該頻道的名字由他名字的縮寫「MKB」和[[高清|高清]]（'''H'''igh '''D'''efinition）的縮寫「HD」組成<ref name=autogenerated2/>，截止2020年1月，擁有超過1,000萬名訂閱者<ref>{{Cite web|title=Marques Brownlee YouTube Channel Analytics and Report|url=https://www.noxinfluencer.com/youtube/channel/UCBJycsmduvYEL83R_U4JriQ?utm_source=facebook|accessdate=2019-06-17|work=www.noxinfluencer.com|language=en|archive-date=2019-06-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190617100547/https://www.noxinfluencer.com/youtube/channel/UCBJycsmduvYEL83R_U4JriQ%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook|dead-url=no}}</ref>，在YouTube科技頻道中訂閱者數量排名第三<ref>{{cite av media|url=https://www.youtube.com/mkbhd|title=Marques Brownlee|work=YouTube}} {{Wayback|url=https://www.youtube.com/mkbhd |date=20210416174006 }}</ref>，有超過8.34億點擊率<ref name=sbyr>{{cite web|url=http://socialblade.com/youtube/user/Marques%20Brownlee|title=Marquesbrownlee YouTube Stats, Channel Statistics - Socialblade.com|work=socialblade.com|access-date=2016-01-18|archive-date=2015-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151012061516/http://socialblade.com/youtube/user/marques%20brownlee|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="milli">{{cite web|url=http://www.stevens.edu/news/content/howe-students-first-million-tech-reviewers-youtube-following-reaches-major-milestone|title=Howe Student's First Million: Tech Reviewer's YouTube Following Reaches Major Milestone|work=stevens.edu|access-date=2016-01-18|archive-date=2016-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307215508/http://www.stevens.edu/news/content/howe-students-first-million-tech-reviewers-youtube-following-reaches-major-milestone|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2013年8月，[[Google|Google]]前社交網絡高級副總裁{{le|維克·岡多特拉|Vic Gundotra}}<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.zdnet.com/blog/perlow/google-real-name-clampdown-ignores-own-grace-period/18299 |title=Google+ real name clampdown ignores own grace period |first=Scott |last=Raymond |publisher=ZDNet |date=August 24, 2011 |quote=It should be pointed out that Vic Gundotra is the Senior Vice-President of Social Business at Google. |access-date=2016-01-18 |archive-date=2014-10-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141022112021/http://www.zdnet.com/blog/perlow/google-real-name-clampdown-ignores-own-grace-period/18299 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.google.com/about/company/facts/management/|title=Management team|work=google.com|accessdate=2016-01-18|archive-date=2012-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121230160111/http://www.google.com/about/company/facts/management/|dead-url=no}}</ref>稱布朗利是「［這個］行星上最好的科技評論員」<ref name=autogenerated2 /><ref name=autogenerated1 />。

== YouTube 生涯 ==
布朗利於2008年3月21日加入YouTube。他於2009年1月仍在讀高中時開始上傳關於新產品，或他已經擁有產品的評論影片<ref name="milli"/><ref name = droida>[http://www.droid-life.com/2013/01/24/the-tato-show-after-hours-episode-2-starts-tonight-at-7pm-pst/ The Tato Show: After Hours – Episode 2] {{Wayback|url=http://www.droid-life.com/2013/01/24/the-tato-show-after-hours-episode-2-starts-tonight-at-7pm-pst/ |date=20201127090816 }} "We will also have a very special guest, Mr. Marques Brownlee who runs the YouTube channel MKBHD. "</ref>。他說他早期的「短片」只是他在[[螢幕錄影|屏幕錄製]]上加入旁白，然後問看影片的人他們想看的內容<ref name = droida/><ref>{{Cite news|url = http://www.businessinsider.com/marques-brownlee-mkdhb-youtube-story-gadget-reviews-2014-11|title = How A Black 20-Year-Old College Student Became 'The Best Technology Reviewer On The Planet'|last = Wei|first = Will|date = November 21, 2014|work = |accessdate = December 17, 2014|archive-date = 2020-01-03|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200103215832/https://www.businessinsider.com/marques-brownlee-mkdhb-youtube-story-gadget-reviews-2014-11|dead-url = no}}</ref>。他首數百段影片主要是關於硬件教學和[[免費軟件|免費軟件]]<ref name="autogenerated2"/>。其後有公司聯絡他，想他在他的影片中示範他們的付費軟硬件，但是他只會就那些對他觀眾有興趣的產品製作評論影片<ref name=autogenerated2 />。他以回應影片觀眾的問題、解釋他們想了解更多的功能和「對他討論的產品有深入的了解，和了解他受眾想學習的東西」著稱<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.stevens.edu/news/content/recording-artist-stevens-students-tech-focused-youtube-channel-draws-millions-subscribers|title=Recording Artist: Stevens Student's Tech-Focused YouTube Channel Draws Millions of Viewers|work=stevens.edu|access-date=2016-01-24|archive-date=2015-12-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151229203222/http://www.stevens.edu/news/content/recording-artist-stevens-students-tech-focused-youtube-channel-draws-millions-subscribers|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他的評論影片通常在產品推出同時或其後不久後上傳，而他關於[[行動裝置|行動裝置]]的影片最為人所知。{{as of|2015|12}}，他的頻道有超過300萬訂閱者<ref name=sbyr/>，使它成為YouTube科技頻道中訂閱者數量排行第三，而他平均每星期上載一段短片。{{as of|2015|7}}，他的頻道每天有2千名新訂閱者<ref>{{cite web|url=http://vidstatsx.com/marquesbrownlee/youtube-channel|title=VidStatsX|access-date=2016-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160105143411/http://vidstatsx.com/marquesbrownlee/youtube-channel|archive-date=2016-01-05|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

其他科技網站亦有報導布朗利的產品評測。[[Engadget|Engadget]]在2012年1月發佈關於布朗利對[[雲端儲存|雲端儲存]]服務Insync評論影片的文章<ref>[http://www.engadget.com/2012/01/04/insync-wave-bye-bye-bye-to-dropbox/ Insync: Wave 'Bye, Bye, Bye' to Dropbox] {{Wayback|url=http://www.engadget.com/2012/01/04/insync-wave-bye-bye-bye-to-dropbox/ |date=20180920011154 }}, Daniel Cooper. January 4, 2012.</ref>。2013年11月，Engadget亦對布朗利關於{{le|LG G Flex}}的影片發佈了文章<ref>[http://www.engadget.com/2013/11/26/lg-g-flex-hands-on/ Hands-on with the G Flex, LG's first curved smartphone] {{Wayback|url=http://www.engadget.com/2013/11/26/lg-g-flex-hands-on/ |date=20190209060942 }} Brad Molen. November 26, 2013.</ref>，在影片中他嘗試刮花該裝置，以測試手機的自癒功能<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.droid-life.com/2013/11/19/mkbhd-goes-hands-on-with-lg-g-flex-self-healing-back-even-takes-a-knife-to-it/|title=MKBHD Goes Hands-on With LG G Flex Self Healing Back, Even Takes a Knife to it|work=droid-life.com|access-date=2016-01-24|archive-date=2021-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118020025/https://www.droid-life.com/2013/11/19/mkbhd-goes-hands-on-with-lg-g-flex-self-healing-back-even-takes-a-knife-to-it/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該影片在第一天已達到了100萬點擊率，而{{As of|2015|9}}，該影片的點擊率已累積超過500萬<ref>[http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Z-W66HINFLg LG G Flex Self Healing Demo] {{Wayback|url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Z-W66HINFLg |date=20210408040014 }} by Marques Brownlee.</ref>。2013年12月，布朗利訪問了[[摩托羅拉移動|摩托羅拉移動]]總裁{{le|丹尼斯·伍德賽德|Dennis Woodside}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.androidauthority.com/moto-ceo-interview-mkbhd-322880/|title=Motorola CEO talks about Project Ara, wearable devices, and Moto X|work=Android Authority|access-date=2016-01-24|archive-date=2020-01-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200103215813/https://www.androidauthority.com/moto-ceo-interview-mkbhd-322880/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>[http://www.engadget.com/2013/12/07/project-ara-moto-maker/ Motorola's modular phone prototype is almost ready, final product might be sold on Moto Maker] {{Wayback|url=http://www.engadget.com/2013/12/07/project-ara-moto-maker/ |date=20190530011126 }} Sean Buckley. December 7, 2013.</ref>。2014年5月，布朗利訪問了[[埃文·布拉斯|埃文·布拉斯]]（{{lang|en|evleaks}}），是布拉斯首次被人訪問<ref>{{cite web |url=http://evleaks.at/2014/05/23/first-evleaks-podcast-fireside-chat-mkbhd/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=1970-01-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140805231352/http://evleaks.at/2014/05/23/first-evleaks-podcast-fireside-chat-mkbhd/ |archivedate=2014-08-05 }}</ref>。

布朗利最受歡迎的影片是在2014年7月7日對傳聞是iPhone 6的玻璃組件的刮花測試。該影片在短時間內被[[The_Verge|The Verge]]、[[福布斯|福布斯]]、[[CNET|CNET]]、[[時代_(雜誌)|時代]]和[[哈芬登郵報|哈芬登郵報]]等網站轉載。該網站出現在[[NBC新聞|NBC新聞]]中，全球各地的報章亦有報導。{{as of|2015|6}}，該影片有超過850萬次點擊率。布朗利亦上載了一段關於iPhone 6模型的影片，{{as of|2015|7}}有700萬點擊率。

2015年12月，布朗利訪問[[NBA|NBA]]運動員[[高比·拜仁|高比·拜仁]]，討論了他對科技的興趣及他參與設計的新球鞋<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dP5Au3tH448 |date=14 December 2015 |title=Talking Tech with Kobe Bryant! |work=MKBHD Channel |access-date=2016-01-24 |archive-date=2021-04-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210424193235/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dP5Au3tH448 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2019年12月，布朗利的YouTube频道订阅人数达到1000万。在其纪念自己1000万订阅的视频中公布了自己的中间名“ Keith ”。<ref>{{Cite video|title=10,000,000!|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NvQmi_ciL1k|website=[[YouTube|YouTube]]|last=Brownlee|first=Marques|access-date=December 18, 2019}} {{Wayback|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NvQmi_ciL1k |date=20201221183106 }}</ref>

